Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:36.88,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}胸の奥のドアを不意にノックする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:49.60,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}振り返る暇もなく 何かに追われ忘れていた景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:56.28,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}今君の声が思い出させるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:10:00.35,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}大丈夫 さあ 始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:04.00,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}And it's the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.99,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}歩き出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:09.50,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}Yeah it's the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.97,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}恐れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:18.24,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}ほら あの丘を越えた場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.86,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}僕を待っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:33.65,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}例えどんなつらい時もその言葉が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:45.90,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}広い海を迷わず進む希望になる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:57.96,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}目の前の暗闇に立ちすくむ度 光をくれるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:08.89,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}もし君が一人を感じる時は 大丈夫 傍にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:12.51,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}And it's the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.54,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}歩き出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:18.25,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}Yeah it's the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.54,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}恐れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:26.54,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}ほら あの丘を越えた場所を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:31.46,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}共に 見に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:41.58,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}形のない木陰に 戸惑う日も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:48.22,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}小さな声でそっとつぶやくのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:54.53,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}君と僕に聞こえる声で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:58.22,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}And it's the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.23,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}歩き出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:04.00,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}Yeah it's the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:06.30,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}恐れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:12.44,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}ほら あの丘を越えた場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:16.97,chaqu-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}僕らを待っているよ
